      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，QuestDB也是开发环境用的，应该和code-server、Grafana一样归到toDevelop类。另外Nginx和Certbot是基础设施，保持默认样式就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
